  <div class="demo">
    <h1 id="heading">These are the details</h1>
    <details>
      <summary>Analytics</summary>
      <p>There are some important 
        There are some important things you should know about certain technologies, such as Analytics. </p>
      <div>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="#dashboard-link">Dashboard</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#reports-link">Reports</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="#datasources-link">Data souces</a>
        </li>
